{
  "stem": "21812.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not every building had that kind of a courtyard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was a very big thing for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, I-- because I loved to build.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, when my young son was about eight years-- oh, maybe, eight-- I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Seven or eight.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I found out that Vienna still had those sets.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were still making them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I wrote to a cousin of mine who lives there now and went back after the war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I told her to buy it for me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And of course, I bought the largest one that existed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, my, my dream.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so I remember I was very excited and hoping that my younger son would be as interested in it as I was.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he used it a little bit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But then I, eventually, when he was sick, I built him an enormous carousel.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I think that was about the last either one of us did with it, but my wish had been fulfilled.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, not very much because-- I did go to the theater a few times, and that I loved.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Actually, I don't remember going to a concert.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And chances are, I wouldn't have it at that age.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But also because, as I said before, at age 10, 11, my father-- the depression was at its worst, and we really couldn't afford to, to buy tickets.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the last thing in a world that, that-- enough difficulty to just put food on the table.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, of course, year later, Hitler-- a couple years later, Hitler came in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So there wasn't much of a chance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I did go to the theater.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I still remember my first play, which was which I enjoyed enormously.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
